也可能关闭，甚至 Android Gerrit 也可能会关闭。 从今往后，只有 Google 内部的员工能够访问 AOSP 的内部分支，或是提交代码。Android 的开发过程将不再透明。"},"attached_info":"CkoIjqKei52/771EEAMaCTExNDE5NjIwNSCHspO/BjAAOLIBQANyEzE4ODg1NzM1MjI5NDg4OTEzMzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"395 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f4b01f0a673279704bab3c074a03559b_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1743063803.880565","card_id":"Q_15645883096","target":{"id":15645883096,"title":"男子 200 多万买二手房遇「20 年租约」，该找谁追责？租约比买卖合同更有效吗？如何查房屋出租情况？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15645883096","type":"question","created":1742774206,"answer_count":60,"follower_count":219,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[14282,27987,28125],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“我花200多万买的房，装修时突然冒出一个持有20年租约的陌生人。”近日，成都市民李先生向媒体爆料，他通过房产中介“到家了”购买的二手房，遭遇“一房两绑”困局——前业主在房屋过户前竟秘密签订超长租约，中介公司被指未尽审查义务。对于查询房屋租赁备案是否为卖房的“必选项”，中介从业者对此说法不一。 200多万买的二手房遭遇“20年租约”！200多万买二手房遇“20年租约”续：住建部门约谈企业，中介公司内部整改"},"attached_info":"CkIIjqKei52/771EEAMaCTExNDEzOTMxNCC+v4K/BjAAONsBQARyCzE1NjQ1ODgzMDk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"353 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-db618fd35cc6812166a32a2efb7a0627_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1743063803.881263","card_id":"Q_1888531207840560914","target":{"id":1888531207840561000,"title":"《复仇者联盟 5》新阵容公布，雷神、黑人美队在列，小罗伯特·唐尼回归饰演末日博士，哪些内容值得期待？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888531207840560914","type":"question","created":1743040927,"answer_count":61,"follower_count":82,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[191159,656582,974795,1351587,2566308],"comment_count":0,"